#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
sleep_detection.py — Factory Floor Worker Sleep / Prolonged-Inactivity Detection
================================================================================
MVP single-file pipeline:
  1. RTMDet-Tiny  →  detect person bounding boxes
  2. Centroid-distance tracker  →  assign persistent person_id across frames
  3. Stillness check  →  centroid movement < MOVEMENT_EPSILON_PX accumulates stillness_duration
  4. RTMPose-S (top-down)  →  run pose estimation on STILL_CANDIDATE person crops
  5. Posture check  →  head-down angle & torso angle vs vertical
  6. State machine  →  NORMAL → STILL_CANDIDATE → POSTURE_CONFIRMED → COOLDOWN → NORMAL
  7. Annotated MP4 output + console logging + sleep_events.log

Tunable constants are at the top of this file (search "CONSTANTS").
"""

